## 封装加载图片的promise  
```js
let loadImg = (src)=>{
    return new Promise((resolve, reject)=>{
        // write your code here
    })
}
```

student_answer:
let loadImg = (src)=>{
    return new Promise((resolve, reject)=>{
        // write your code here
       let image = new Image();
            image.onload = function(){
                resolve(); 
            };
            image.onerror = function(){
                reject(new Error('Could not load image '));
            };

        });

}
